partnerDetails.about: Multi-pack was established in 1986 as a small concern, catering to the requirements of local engineering companies. With determination, vision and expansion the company grew to a major competitor in the market place. Multi-pack offers you quality, service and commitment, providing you with the most effective way of a full service packaging solution to protect your valuable product.
